Description: ConnectIT Networks is an innovative business technology support and service company.
Headquarters Regions: West Coast, Western US
Full Description: The company was founded as Desert Sky Networks & Communications, Inc. and is a Managed Services Provider (MSP) and Information Technology consulting, support & service firm serving customers in the Portland, Oregon/Vancouver, Washington areas of the Pacific Northwest with top quality technicians, management and technology partners who have a keen interest in customer satisfaction and growing their business. Desert Sky Networks & Communications, Inc. was started in February 2006 and was incorporated in the state of Nevada in August of 2006, and provided IT support for businesses in the Las Vegas metro area until October 2006 when the company relocated to the Pacific Northwest to offer data & networking services to the market in the Pacific Northwest. In continued business growth Desert sky Networks expanded the hosting services in February 2009 as ConnectIT Networks, Inc. to include Microsoft Exchange 2007 Enterprise hosting, and upgraded the entire data center servers and E-Mail and Website hosting offerings. At the end of the 2nd quarter 2009 ConnectIT Networks, Inc. started to deploy Outsourced IT and Managed Services platforms, and well as hosted Virtual SaaS (Software as a service) services. As of the 4th quarter 2009 the company deployed a complete Managed Services, Remote Monitoring & Reporting services offering. ConnectIT Networks, Inc. provides complete network managed services for businesses including providing server, desktop & device monitoring and alerting, IT network reporting, Network & Server virtualization, help desk support including remote and on-site assistance, systems updating and patch management, Network Policy management & enforcement, Computer & Network Inventory/Audits, Network and Data security, Data Backup and Disaster recovery, EMail & Microsoft Exchange 2007 hosting, Website hosting, VoIP (Voice over IP) PBX communications hosting & SaaS (Software as a Service) Hosting. ConnectIT Networks, Inc. has strong technology partnerships with industry leaders such as Cisco Systems, Dell Computers, Microsoft, Barracuda Networks, Kaspersky Labs, Acronis, VMWare, Panterra Networks & N-able Technologies. Desert Sky Networks will continue to utilize and leverage these strong relationships to provide the highest quality of support, service and technical expertise to their customers. ConnectIT Networks, Inc. is an innovative business technology support and service company based on the belief that a MSP (Managed Service Provider) can provide quality outsourced IT (Information Technology) support and service to companies who operate or need to operate their business electronically. ConnectIT Networks, Inc. will provide continual network and systems monitoring & reporting for it's customers, as well as remote help desk support and on-site support services. ConnectIT Networks, Inc. also will provide quality E-Mail, Website & Microsoft Exchange hosting services from it's data center hosted in Vancouver, Washington, USA. Added to the service offerings to it's customers Desert Sky Networks will provide SaaS (Software as a Service), Virtualization, Data backup with cloud storage, and hosted VoIP (Voice over IP) resell services. As a Cisco Systems Select Certified Partner with over 4 years of business partner certification, and over a combined 15 years of Cisco Systems experience and certifications from the Company's management team, ConnectIT Networks, Inc. has already positioned itself as one of the leading Cisco Systems SMB partners in the Northwest United States. As a Outsourced IT department for it's customers ConnectIT Networks, Inc. looks to also grow its sales numbers with Cisco Systems and to be able to provide solid and effective network reliability and service for the networks the company designs and maintains.
